439
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:52,800
'Please don't tell anyone,' she said.

440
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:55,680
'I come here to talk to my mom and dad.

441
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,200
Is that stupid?'

442
00:24:57,200 --> 00:25:01,080
'No, it isn't stupid,' Clark said.

443
00:25:01,080 --> 00:25:02,720
'Do you remember them?'

